Package it.unimi.dsi.fastutil.bytes

Class ByteObjectMutablePair<V>

java.lang.Object
it.unimi.dsi.fastutil.bytes.ByteObjectMutablePair<V>
All Implemented Interfaces:
ByteObjectPair<V>, Pair<Byte,V>, Serializable
public class ByteObjectMutablePair<V> extends Object implements ByteObjectPair<V>, Serializable
A type-specific mutable Pair; provides some additional methods that use polymorphism to avoid (un)boxing.
